{"tid":305548,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE] 評論「I go to school by bus」太低分 老師教一招變5等級寫法","createTime":"2017-07-01T17:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T10:40:46.000Z","uid":97598,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe55d009dbfb416d3dc121b90252aa507556aad","tid":305548,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBw1ZEANt&amp;p=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3DABFGD1owBw1ZEANt%26p%3D1&d=9LR%2Fd9nD%2FHm%2BSBfe%2FRu7G9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=20fe6595\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBw1ZEANt&amp;p=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/002650_64a3ae761f10954b365c82d6dbfc04d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F002650_64a3ae761f10954b365c82d6dbfc04d9.png&h=ec5309eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/002700_1f61afd0daf5bb7f40c3e2d2356c78a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F002700_1f61afd0daf5bb7f40c3e2d2356c78a0.png&h=82b8db00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/002706_ca2e06d86238d5ce4b556cea5809f345.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F002706_ca2e06d86238d5ce4b556cea5809f345.png&h=bfd5abc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先利申: DSE Eng 5** + Writing 5**<br />\n上星期網上有好多針對DSE英文科同嗰位老師嘅comments, 不過有幾個位我見冇乜人講所以我想補充少少。<br />\n<br />\n第一點其實十分簡單。DSE Writing係根據<span style=\"color: red;\">整篇作文</span>比分, 並不是根據整篇作文當中嘅某一句比分。所以我唔明白點解嗰位老師可以斷言A句係Lv2, B句係Lv5。句字嘅寫法固然可以分高低, 但係作文Lv一定唔係咁比, 而係根據overall performance。就算係佔7分嘅Language分, 我都係要based on overall language, 而並不是某一句嘅language。<br />\n<br />\n第二點其實有人提出過, 我想加少少補充。我個人認為某部分人對DSE Writing有錯誤嘅理解(當然如果係諷刺嗰位老師就另計)。該部分人認為DSE Writing其實就係迫學生要用多啲深字深phrase先高分。呢句statement其實係與事實不符, 講法並不公道。考評局每年report都批評呢種行文方式, 某一兩年甚至比埋examples話比你聽點解唔好。而少用深字但高分嘅例子有好多, 大家可以上HKEAA睇考生示例。<br />\n<br />\n第三點非常重要, 想補充番第二點「用深字深phrase」呢個位。大家要記住: <span style=\"color: red;\">深唔係錯; 深但係用得唔啱先係錯</span>, 而HKEAA report所例舉嘅係深但係用得唔啱嘅例子。某部分人倒返轉頭話字要simple、句子要simple先係好, 我個人認為呢個concept都係唔正確。<span style=\"color: red;\">能否準確表達意思、是否合乎場合/語境需要</span>先係決定用字嘅準則。簡言之, 我認為作文唔係要追求「深」, 亦唔係要追求「淺」。所以po secret嗰位同學要比埋前文後理、語境、題目等等資料我先可以再進一步評論。話唔定同學同老師嘅寫法放返入文章睇係唔好。<br />\n<br />\n第四點其實唔關篇secret事, 涉及到點學新字/phrase。學新生字/phrase就好似玩online game咁。玩online game打怪正常你唔會一嚟就挑王、打高Lv怪, 你要慢慢打同自己Lv相應嘅怪, 一路打上去吸經升Lv, 然後先挑王、打高Lv怪。同理, 學新生字/phrase係要啲背誦, 但係要由淺入深。補習社比材料你讀係好事, 但係notes只得一份而不是tailor-made for每位同學, 所以大家都應該根據自己能力挑選合適嘅讀。"},{"pid":"1eb0a6ea1158f13e6a09fd12af534e13ab9c0ab4","tid":305548,"uid":97598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:58:48.000Z","msg":"就住第二點所講, 我得閒會po學生示例分析一吓。"},{"pid":"5df12471eca63f5a3f745d845529186fa1160bf0","tid":305548,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:00:49.000Z","msg":"有幾複雜 睇過scmp standard啲報紙未 睇過白官發表啲speech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dc934e9aa724c5c4ffbcb7ab7e38125fe9edec","tid":305548,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾複雜 睇過scmp standard啲報紙未 睇過白官發表啲speech未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0b66aa2bb3ceda96f381ab17f6107f3e086b6196","tid":305548,"uid":125938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:04:38.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bba9f2e6772c8639284d83b0b511522ba3b8c83","tid":305548,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾複雜 睇過scmp standard啲報紙未 睇過白官發表啲speech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰啲反而我個人認為唔深, 只係用字比較formal。當然深淺一來好主觀, 二來都只係相對其他字而言。<br />\n我反而覺得一般同學寫唔出好嘅semi-formal/informal嘅writing, 例如blog, personal letter。"},{"pid":"3eb60ee70d0f86fc49c6d1b98f522fee914ba839","tid":305548,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾複雜 睇過scmp standard啲報紙未 睇過白官發表啲speech <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰啲反而我個人認為唔深, 只係用字比較formal。當然深淺一來好主觀, 二來都只係相對其他字而言。<br />\n我反而覺得一般同學寫唔出好嘅semi-formal/informal嘅writing, 例如blog, personal letter。</blockquote><br />\n曬氣啦你"},{"pid":"c0f64218b3974d33cf2b11c7c569335971e872f3","tid":305548,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T21:31:51.000Z","msg":"The preferred method of my daily transport method to school would likely to be public transport. On a non daily basis, personal transport can be more preferable due to the lack of available time.<br />\n<br />\nI usually go to school by bus."},{"pid":"5c8360d300ccc28d9a2cfed4de82390c26269d41","tid":305548,"uid":97598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"2012 Q.1 (Exemplar 1)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/114049_3a6d14b9bacc03a504bdfb21f02e7f05.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F114049_3a6d14b9bacc03a504bdfb21f02e7f05.JPG&h=42b4a5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/114055_2bfc43a6e29b7ac8ce75fd9da690be68.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F114055_2bfc43a6e29b7ac8ce75fd9da690be68.JPG&h=37148554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/114101_aedc358f540ee075e1fcd4130de3ba0a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F114101_aedc358f540ee075e1fcd4130de3ba0a.JPG&h=b0ad73cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/114106_f3d1da6d3f513920e9e4e672d59c01ee.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F114106_f3d1da6d3f513920e9e4e672d59c01ee.JPG&h=85fa2a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/114113_4a298f10da57ebc1cd97f0f2238b76f3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F114113_4a298f10da57ebc1cd97f0f2238b76f3.JPG&h=718cef34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢份sample官方話屬於Lv5 or above, 不過你可以見到comment用嘅字眼, i.e. entirely, totally, 其實暗示佢每一個domain嘅分數相當高(Language應該無7, 其餘有7), 所以我估計佢其實拎5**。<br />\n<br />\n呢篇作文用字真係完全唔深, 大致上準確。而佢文法並非全對, 但亦已經十分準確, 瑕不掩瑜。正如我之前話, 評價一篇作文唔能夠只單靠某一兩句句子下判斷。如果根據secret入面嗰位老師嘅說法, 呢篇文章Lv5都未必有。因此我懷疑嗰位老師唔瞭解考評局嘅評分標準。<br />\n<br />\n跟住我想講啲值得向呢篇作文學習嘅位置。<br />\nSit at the office --&gt; in the office vs at the office有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\ntravel with my crew--&gt;學下嗰crew字嘅用法。唔洗每次都用&quot;team&quot;。<br />\n<br />\ndid the best--&gt; try my/the best vs do my/the best<br />\n<br />\nget together<br />\n<br />\ngot married with someone<br />\n<br />\nenjoy + gerund<br />\n<br />\n以上items我相信大家一定應付到。"},{"pid":"814596efebd0a1bc503512c519c93fae78b6c517","tid":305548,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa912dea1f9d70662968675081fb0840b092a7d","tid":305548,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"2013 Part A Lv4 Exemplar 2 (Photo B)<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/181549_db11337d337664b9ebd2c9a811deb2f3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F181549_db11337d337664b9ebd2c9a811deb2f3.JPG&h=45ef1f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/181556_8f73a5519ae3d1fc6d5c4965cf81c36a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F181556_8f73a5519ae3d1fc6d5c4965cf81c36a.JPG&h=fc9a3745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/181940_0cb96f492e3d589fba2383100e3b38c6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F181940_0cb96f492e3d589fba2383100e3b38c6.JPG&h=5cf0b51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢篇作文連同Photo A一齊被評為Lv4。呢篇作文用嘅vocab水平對於乜柒都叻嘅連登仔嚟講當然唔深, 例如frustrated, cope with, intervened, grievance(佢串錯字), tailor-made, obstacles, conquerable, collaboration, encouragement等等。雖然唔深, 不過都叫做有啲嘢睇下。我想大家明白, 呢種水平嘅生字已經足夠拎5**,  只係文法都好重要。佢文法太差所以拖低Language, 而且內容好明顯有偏離, 所以拎唔到Lv5係十分合理。希望藉呢篇作文提醒大家Basic grammar同扣題嘅重要性。"}]}